N_{L/K}(1+x) \in \mathcal{O}
N_{L/K}
\sigma_i:L \to \overline{K}
\mathcal{O}
\{x:|x|_K \leq 1\}
|\cdot|_K
K
N_{L/K}(1+x)=\prod_{i=1}^n \sigma_i(1+x)=\prod_{i=1}^n (\sigma_i(1)+\sigma_i(x))=\prod_{i=1}^n (1+\sigma_i(x))
= \prod_{i=1}^n \sigma_i(x)+\sum_{j=1}^n \prod_{i\neq j} \sigma_i(x) + \sum_{j=1}^n \sum_{k=1}^n \prod_{i\neq j,k} \sigma_i(x)+\ldots +1
\prod_{i=1}^n \sigma_i(x)=N_{L/K}(x)
N_{L/K}(x)
